in Israeli airstrikes on southern Lebanon.</p> <p>The sources indicated that one person was killed in an Israeli drone strike that targeted a car in the town of Zrarieh, while two airstrikes on the town of Tayr Dibba resulted in injuries to paramedics.</p> <p>They explained that Israeli aircraft also launched an airstrike on the town of Hadatha in the Bint Jbeil district, and another airstrike on the Jabal al-Rafie area between the towns of Siddiqin and Jabal al-Batoum in the Tyre district. (QNA)</p> <p>The Israeli entity continues its attacks on southern Lebanon, despite the announcement of a second 45-day extension of the ceasefire on Friday.</p>", "content": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "keywords": ["the peninsula", "988", "qatar"], "creator": ["the peninsula newspaper"], "language": "english", "country": ["algeria", "mauritania", "israel", "syria", "somalia", "libya", "cyprus", "azerbaijan", "yemen", "georgia", "afghanistan", "sudan", "uzbekistan", "iran", "djibouti", "saudi arabia", "turkey", "bahrain", "jordan", "pakistan", "armenia", "oman", "united arab emirates", "kuwait", "ethiopia", "qatar", "kazakhstan", "tunisia", "india", "morocco", "turkmenistan", "kyrgyzstan", "tajikistan", "iraq", "lebanon", "egypt"], "category": ["top", "crime"], "datatype": "news", "pubDate": "2026-05-17 16:34:28", "pubDateTZ": "UTC", "fetched_at": "2026-05-17 17:06:50", "image_url": "https://thepeninsulaqatar.com/get/maximage/20260517_1779035797-883.PNG?1779035798", "video_url": null, "source_id": "thepeninsulaqatar", "source_name": "The Peninsula Qatar", "source_priority": 52716, "source_url": "https://thepeninsulaqatar.com", "source_icon": "https://n.bytvi.com/thepeninsulaqatar.png", "sentiment": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "sentiment_stats": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_tag": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_region": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_org": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE PLA